item.title: Travel to ShaoHai Park in CNY
item.description: This new year was the coldest in Qingdao since I first went here in 2016. The coldest day is -16 degrees celsius, and I can only spend all the time inside the room. To my disappointment, I thought it would be snow stack and no. Before I left, the cold air left then sunlight made the ground warm, the highest weather was 8 degrees celsius, so I decided to leave the cozy room and travel to the well-known park in JiaoZhou: ShaoHai Park.
